  "content": {
    "text": "Selamat Datang! ðŸ‘‹ Panduan interaktif FFmpeg untuk audio/video. Pilih topik di menu sebelah kiri untuk melihat berbagai perintah yang bisa dicoba. Klik tombol \"Salin\" untuk menyalin perintah langsung ke clipboard. Ubah Format Audio MP3 â†’ OGG Konversi file `.mp3` ke `.ogg` dengan FFmpeg. Salin ffmpeg -i input.mp3 output.ogg Batch Convert Audio Ubah semua file `.mp3` dalam folder menjadi `.ogg` sekaligus. Salin for f in *.mp3; do ffmpeg -i \"$f\" \"${f%.mp3}.ogg\"; done WAV â†’ MP3 Salin ffmpeg -i input.wav -codec:a libmp3lame -qscale:a 2 output.mp3 Change Audio Bitrate Salin ffmpeg -i input.mp3 -b:a 192k output.mp3 Normalize Audio Salin ffmpeg -i input.mp3 -af \"loudnorm\" output.mp3 Trim Video Salin ffmpeg -i input.mp4 -ss 00:00:10 -to 00:00:20 -c copy output.mp4 Resize Video Salin ffmpeg -i input.mp4 -vf scale=1280:720 output.mp4 Extract Audio Salin ffmpeg -i input.mp4 -q:a 0 -map a output.mp3 Convert MP4 â†’ WebM Salin ffmpeg -i input.mp4 -c:v libvpx -b:v 1M -c:a libvorbis output.webm Batch Convert Video Salin for f in *.mov; do ffmpeg -i \"$f\" -c:v libx264 -crf 23 -c:a aac \"${f%.mov}.mp4\"; done",
    "html": "<div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row min-h-screen\">\n  \n\n  <main id=\"content-display\" class=\"w-full md:ml-[25%] lg:ml-[20%] p-6 md:p-10\"></main>\n</div>\n\n<!-- Templates -->\n<template id=\"welcome-content\">\n<div class=\"bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm\">\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4\">Selamat Datang! ðŸ‘‹</h2>\n<p class=\"text-lg text-gray-600 mb-4\">Panduan interaktif FFmpeg untuk audio/video. Pilih topik di menu sebelah kiri untuk melihat berbagai perintah yang bisa dicoba.</p>\n<p class=\"text-gray-600\">Klik tombol \"Salin\" untuk menyalin perintah langsung ke clipboard.</p>\n</div>\n</template>\n\n<template id=\"ffmpeg-convert-content\">\n<div class=\"bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm\">\n<h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2\">Ubah Format Audio MP3 â†’ OGG</h2>\n<p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Konversi file `.mp3` ke `.ogg` dengan FFmpeg.</p>\n<div class=\"code-block\">\n<button class=\"copy-btn\">Salin</button>\n<pre><code>ffmpeg -i input.mp3 output.ogg</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div></template>\n\n<template id=\"ffmpeg-batch-content\">\n<div class=\"bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm\">\n<h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2\">Batch Convert Audio</h2>\n<p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-4\">Ubah semua file `.mp3` dalam folder menjadi `.ogg` sekaligus.</p>\n<div class=\"code-block\">\n<button class=\"copy-btn\">Salin</button>\n<pre><code>for f in *.mp3; do ffmpeg -i \"$f\" \"${f%.mp3}.ogg\"; done</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div></template>\n\n<template id=\"ffmpeg-wav-mp3-content\">\n<div class=\"bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm\">\n<h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2\">WAV â†’ MP3</h2>\n<div class=\"code-block\">\n<button class=\"copy-btn\">Salin</button>\n<pre><code>ffmpeg -i input.wav -codec:a libmp3lame -qscale:a 2 output.mp3</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div></template>\n\n<template id=\"ffmpeg-audio-bitrate-content\">\n<div class=\"bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm\">\n<h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2\">Change Audio Bitrate</h2>\n<div class=\"code-block\">\n<button class=\"copy-btn\">Salin</button>\n<pre><code>ffmpeg -i input.mp3 -b:a 192k output.mp3</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div></template>\n\n<template id=\"ffmpeg-normalize-content\">\n<div class=\"bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm\">\n<h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2\">Normalize Audio</h2>\n<div class=\"code-block\">\n<button class=\"copy-btn\">Salin</button>\n<pre><code>ffmpeg -i input.mp3 -af \"loudnorm\" output.mp3</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div></template>\n\n<template id=\"ffmpeg-trim-content\">\n<div class=\"bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm\">\n<h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2\">Trim Video</h2>\n<div class=\"code-block\">\n<button class=\"copy-btn\">Salin</button>\n<pre><code>ffmpeg -i input.mp4 -ss 00:00:10 -to 00:00:20 -c copy output.mp4</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div></template>\n\n<template id=\"ffmpeg-resize-content\">\n<div class=\"bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm\">\n<h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2\">Resize Video</h2>\n<div class=\"code-block\">\n<button class=\"copy-btn\">Salin</button>\n<pre><code>ffmpeg -i input.mp4 -vf scale=1280:720 output.mp4</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div></template>\n\n<template id=\"ffmpeg-extract-audio-content\">\n<div class=\"bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm\">\n<h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2\">Extract Audio</h2>\n<div class=\"code-block\">\n<button class=\"copy-btn\">Salin</button>\n<pre><code>ffmpeg -i input.mp4 -q:a 0 -map a output.mp3</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div></template>\n\n<template id=\"ffmpeg-mp4-webm-content\">\n<div class=\"bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm\">\n<h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2\">Convert MP4 â†’ WebM</h2>\n<div class=\"code-block\">\n<button class=\"copy-btn\">Salin</button>\n<pre><code>ffmpeg -i input.mp4 -c:v libvpx -b:v 1M -c:a libvorbis output.webm</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div></template>\n\n<template id=\"ffmpeg-batch-video-content\">\n<div class=\"bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm\">\n<h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2\">Batch Convert Video</h2>\n<div class=\"code-block\">\n<button class=\"copy-btn\">Salin</button>\n<pre><code>for f in *.mov; do ffmpeg -i \"$f\" -c:v libx264 -crf 23 -c:a aac \"${f%.mov}.mp4\"; done</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div></template>\n\n\n<div class=\"search-floating-container\"><input type=\"text\" id=\"floatingSearchInput\" placeholder=\"cari artikel...\" autocomplete=\"off\"><span id=\"floatingSearchClear\" class=\"clear-button\"></span><div id=\"floatingSearchResults\" class=\"floating-results-container\"></div></div>\n<section id=\"related-marquee-section\"><div id=\"related-marquee-container\"></div></section>"
